emo", "slug": "kpi-with-chart-inline"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"with-footer\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#with-footer\" class=\"peer\">With Footer</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "kpi-with-footer"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"with-icon\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#with-icon\" class=\"peer\">With Icon</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "kpi-with-icon"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"with-progress\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#with-progress\" class=\"peer\">With Progress</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n"}, {"type": "demo", "slug": "kpi-with-progress"}, {"type": "html", "html": "\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"css-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#css-classes\" class=\"peer\">CSS Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"base-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#base-classes\" class=\"peer\">Base Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>.kpi</code> - Base card shell with flex column layout and padding</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"element-classes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#element-classes\" class=\"peer\">Element Classes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>.kpi__header</code> - Top row for icon, title, and actions</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__content</code> - Grid layout container for value and trend side by side</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__icon</code> - Status-tinted icon container</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__actions</code> - Absolutely positioned action button area</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__title</code> - Metric label text (<code>dt</code> element)</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__value</code> - Large formatted number (<code>dd</code> element)</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__trend</code> - Inline trend badge (wraps TrendChip)</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__progress</code> - Full-width progress bar area</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__chart</code> - Sparkline container with edge-fade mask</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__separator</code> - Edge-to-edge divider</li>\n<li><code>.kpi__footer</code> - Bottom section</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"data-attributes\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#data-attributes\" class=\"peer\">Data Attributes</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>[data-status=\"success\"]</code> / <code>[data-status=\"warning\"]</code> / <code>[data-status=\"danger\"]</code> on <code>.kpi__icon</code> - Status color tinting</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"css-variables\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#css-variables\" class=\"peer\">CSS Variables</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>--kpi-chart-fade</code> - Edge fade width for the sparkline mask (default: <code>10%</code>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"api-reference\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#api-reference\" class=\"peer\">API Reference</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h2>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpi\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpi\" class=\"peer\">KPI</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>The root component. Wraps HeroUI <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/card\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Card</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>KPI sub-components</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/card\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HeroUI Card</a> props.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpiheader\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpiheader\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Header</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Top row container for icon, title, and actions.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Icon, Title, and Actions elements</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpicontent\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpicontent\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Content</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Grid layout container placing value and trend side by side.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Value, Trend, Progress, etc.</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpiicon\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpiicon\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Icon</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Status-tinted icon container.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>status</code></td><td><code>'success' | 'warning' | 'danger'</code></td><td>-</td><td>Status color for icon background tinting</td></tr><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Icon element</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpititle\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpititle\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Title</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Metric label rendered as a <code>dt</code> element.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Title text</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>dt</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpivalue\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpivalue\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Value</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Large formatted number display. Wraps <a href=\"#numbervalue\">NumberValue</a> with a <code>dd</code> element for semantics.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>value</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td>-</td><td><strong>Required.</strong> The numeric value to format</td></tr><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>((formatted: string) =&gt; ReactNode)</code></td><td>-</td><td>Optional render function receiving the formatted string</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all NumberValue props except <code>children</code>.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpitrend\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpitrend\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Trend</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Inline trend badge. Wraps <a href=\"#trendchip\">TrendChip</a>.</p>\n<p>Also supports all TrendChip props.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpiprogress\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpiprogress\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Progress</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Full-width progress bar.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>value</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td>-</td><td><strong>Required.</strong> Progress value from 0 to 100</td></tr><tr><td><code>status</code></td><td><code>'success' | 'warning' | 'danger'</code></td><td><code>'success'</code></td><td>Status color for the progress bar</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpiactions\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpiactions\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Actions</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Action button (three-dot icon by default). Wraps HeroUI <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Button</a> as a ghost icon-only button.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Custom icon replacing the default three-dot icon</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/button\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HeroUI Button</a> props.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpichart\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpichart\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Chart</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Sparkline area chart using <a href=\"https://recharts.github.io/en-US/api/AreaChart/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Recharts</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>data</code></td><td><code>Record&lt;string, number | string&gt;[]</code></td><td>-</td><td><strong>Required.</strong> Chart data array</td></tr><tr><td><code>dataKey</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>'value'</code></td><td>Key in each data object to use as the Y value</td></tr><tr><td><code>color</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td><code>'currentColor'</code></td><td>Stroke/line color</td></tr><tr><td><code>fillColor</code></td><td><code>string</code></td><td>-</td><td>Fill color for the area gradient. Defaults to <code>color</code> at 20% opacity</td></tr><tr><td><code>height</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>80</code></td><td>Chart height in pixels</td></tr><tr><td><code>strokeWidth</code></td><td><code>number</code></td><td><code>2</code></td><td>Stroke width</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpiseparator\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpiseparator\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Separator</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Edge-to-edge divider. Wraps HeroUI <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/separator\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Separator</a>.</p>\n<p>Also supports all <a href=\"https://heroui.com/docs/react/components/separator\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">HeroUI Separator</a> props.</p>\n<h3 class=\"flex scroll-m-28 flex-row items-center gap-2\" id=\"kpifooter\"><a data-card=\"\" href=\"#kpifooter\" class=\"peer\">KPI.Footer</a><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link size-3.5 shrink-0 text-fd-muted-foreground opacity-0 transition-opacity peer-hover:opacity-100\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></h3>\n<p>Bottom section for additional details or links.</p>\n<div class=\"relative overflow-auto prose-no-margin my-6\"><table><thead><tr><th>Prop</th><th>Type</th><th>Default</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>children</code></td><td><code>ReactNode</code></td><td>-</td><td>Footer content</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>Also supports all native <code>div</code> HTML attributes.</p></div><div class=\"@container my-8 grid gap-4 grid-cols-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none\" href=\"/docs/react/components/item-card-group\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M10.53 2.97a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06L6.56 8l3.97 3.97a.75.75 0 1 1-1.06 1.06l-4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06l4.5-4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>Item Card Group</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A layout component for grouping item cards in list or grid arrangements with section headers and dividers.</p></a><a class=\"hover:text-fd-accent-foreground hover:bg-surface-secondary @max-lg:col-span-full flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl p-4 text-sm transition-none text-end\" href=\"/docs/react/components/kpi-group\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 font-medium flex-row-reverse\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"-mx-1 size-4 shrink-0 rtl:rotate-180\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.47 13.03a.75.75 0 0 1 0-1.06L9.44 8 5.47 4.03a.75.75 0 0 1 1.06-1.06l4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1 0 1.06l-4.5 4.5a.75.75 0 0 1-1.06 0\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\"></path></svg><p>KPI Group</p></div><p class=\"text-fd-muted-foreground truncate\">A layout component for arranging multiple KPI cards in horizontal or vertical stacks with consistent spacing.</p></a></div>"}], "tocHtml": "<a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#usage\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground scroll-m-4 transition-colors wrap-anywhere first:pt-0 last:pb-0 data-[active=true]:text-fd-primary hover:text-fd-accent-foreground ps-3\">Usage</a><a data-active=\"false\" href=\"#anatomy\" class=\"prose py-1.5 text-sm text-fd-muted-foreground s